.\" KiloNode - Developed by M6VPN (M6VPN@tuta.com)
.\" kilonode/docs/man/kilonodectl.1
.Dd May 26, 2026
.Dt KILONODECTL 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm kilonodectl
.Nd query a local KiloNode daemon control socket
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl -socket Ar path
.Ar command
.Op Ar arguments
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
connects to the local Unix-domain control socket exposed by
.Xr kilonoded 8
and sends one read-only command.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl -socket Ar path
Use the control socket at
.Ar path .
.It Fl -help
Show command usage.
.El
.Sh COMMANDS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Cm ping
Check daemon reachability.
.It Cm status
Show daemon status.
.It Cm ports
Show configured ports.
.It Cm stats
Show daemon counters.
.It Cm heard Op Fl -port Ar name
Show heard AX.25 stations.
.It Cm bbs status | stats | areas | users | messages | message Ar id
Show read-only local BBS state.
.It Cm rx status
Show receive event queue status.
.It Cm rx events Op Fl -limit Ar n | Fl -port Ar name | Fl -from Ar callsign | Fl -to Ar callsign
Show recent receive events.
.It Cm rx event Ar id
Show one receive event.
.It Cm rx sessions Op Fl -port Ar name | Fl -from Ar callsign
Show observed receive-side sessions.
.It Cm tx status
Show transmit policy and queue status.
.It Cm tx queue Op Fl -port Ar name
Show queued outbound frames.
.It Cm tx frame Ar id
Show one queued outbound frame.
.It Cm tx dryrun-ui Fl -port Ar name Fl -from Ar callsign Fl -to Ar callsign Op Fl -via Ar path Fl -text Ar text
Queue a local dry-run UI frame when daemon transmit policy explicitly allows it.
.It Cm tx dispatch-status
Show test-only TX dispatch harness status.
.It Cm tx dispatch-run Op Fl -port Ar name
Run the test-only TX dispatcher when daemon policy and memory targets allow it.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Pa /tmp/kilonode/control.sock
Example local control socket path.
.El
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Dl kilonodectl --socket /tmp/kilonode/control.sock status
.Dl kilonodectl --socket /tmp/kilonode/control.sock bbs messages
.Dl kilonodectl --socket /tmp/kilonode/control.sock rx events
.Dl kilonodectl --socket /tmp/kilonode/control.sock rx sessions
.Dl kilonodectl --socket /tmp/kilonode/control.sock tx status
.Dl kilonodectl --socket /tmp/kilonode/control.sock tx queue
.Dl kilonodectl --socket /tmp/kilonode/control.sock tx dryrun-ui --port kiss0 --from M6VPN-1 --to CQ --text "hello"
.Dl kilonodectl --socket /tmp/kilonode/control.sock tx dispatch-status
.Dl kilonodectl --socket /tmp/kilonode/control.sock tx dispatch-run --port mem0
.Sh SECURITY NOTES
The control protocol is local-only in this pass. Use filesystem permissions to
limit access to the socket. TX dispatch is test-only and memory/mock-only in
this pass.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr kilonoded 8
